message.body: Hey, did you order fios already? I just got a notice from UPS that a package was left at #### from Verizon. (hadn't updated my address with UPS yet)
Yep. Guy should be showing up sunday
Okay, cool. If it's not for you, just toss it. I think they might have mailed me a return kit for my equipment even though I dropped it off.
Safe travels. I am sure ##### and #### will be very happy to see you :-)
They'd better not have trashed the place!
You never know... They are wild little dudes...
